title: 2018 Sales Listings
html_content:
This article is rated M for Honest Content
It may contain content deemed not safe for work. Reader discretion is advised.
“ [The Idea Guys] were telling him what to sell/urging him to dig through more boxes, etc. in an effort to find things to hawk on eBay to make money for them. ”
Guard Dog The Captain.[1]

This page lists the stuff Chris offered for sale in 2018. In addition, he also sold Sonichu comics printed through Lulu via Patreon.

Chris hit his highest amount of sales revenue during this year, exceeding over $10,000 in sales. The sales were heavily influenced by the Idea Guys saga, as they were alleged to have extorted Chris out of $6,000 by threatening to destroy his imaginary city CWCville. To help raise money to pay them off, Chris sold many items, including several of his Transformers toys, his Amnyfest Ring and ShecameforCWC.JPG, as well as random objects from the Chandler home including Cole Smithey's old homework assignments.

Sales continued after April, when the Idea Guys were removed from power, as the Chandlers were still having financial issues. Chris sold more items during the summer such as Sonichu- and Chris Chan-themed autographed photos, cards, and Fanta cans.

Sales from this year would also start the Guard Dogs and Teen Troon Squad sagas, as Guard Dog The Captain began contact with Chris via purchasing his Amnyfest Ring, and Teen Troon Squad members began contact by purchasing shecameforCWC.JPG.

  • Listed 6 March, as Buy It Now

Ticket For Sailor Moon The Musical At Alamo Drafthouse Theater

Winchester, VA, USA

I was going to see this movie with my friends, but we found a theater closer to our location that will also be showing it. And I can’t get a refund for this ticket; purchased it online. It is for Row 4, Seat 1; this is an awesome show. Please help me out. Full ticket will be sent via private message after sale. Thank you.

Note: The show is for 17 March, yet Chris set the eBay listing to end on 5 April. Chris had purchased an aisle seat and the seat next to it was still available, putting into question Chris's claim about wanting to see the show with friends. It's very possible he met someone who was also going to the show but had a closer seat, even though some places, if the seating is open, may allow goers to take a closer seat. He also says he will be going to a showing closer to Ruckersville, even though all current locations for the musical are only slightly closer/way farther than Winchester, meaning Chris will drive 1.5-2 hours just to see a screening (not live) of a Sailor Moon show

It should also be noted that only two seats at this time (3-10, 6:52 PM CST) are taken that are "closer" to the stage- Row 2 seats 8 and 9- even though all the seats are the exact same price of 15 dollars. It should also be noted its far away from other people- the front row and the handicap row behind are clear

  • Listed: 23 April[11]

However, on 24 April, Lukas Simpkins, aka Twitter user FFEMemberLukas, expressed interest in buying the art:

@CWCSonichu im willing to pay the 1,000$ for the drawings, please repost them on ebay or esty so i can

Chris replied:

I can’t relist them; eBay is against that. I sent you a direct message, Lukas.

Lukas insisted on a working link, so Chris then quietly relisted the drawings as "Artsfor lukas," and it quickly sold. Lukas gave credit to Twitter user @wxlfdxg for giving him ideas on buying the set.

The listing included Sonichu 8's infamous sex scene, at least one page from the Giant Penis Comic, and the cut-up remains of ShecameforCWC.JPG. Note how most of the art is censored as well (including Chris's man-nips)

I am selling off, as a lot, all 32 of my past and recently-drawn porn drawings I drew personally over the years, including all of the pieces of the torn up “She Came For CWC” drawing in an envelope. Go ahead, you Pervs! You know you Want to pay Large for this lot directly from me. No Certificate of Authenticity will be included, because All of these drawings only bring me feeling ashamed of myself from my past. No Negotiations and No Returns.

This event would later set up the beginning of the Teen Troon Squad saga.
